    "body": "In the code that you paste, `category` match with `attributeName` and also is present in the Range and not associated with the label so I suppose that something is wrong.\r\n\r\nAlso I checked  [CurrentRefinements#transformItems](https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/blob/v2/packages/react-instantsearch/src/components/CurrentRefinements.js#L16) because maybe I can use this method for make a workaround but currently is not being used in the implementation. Do you think that is a bug?\r\n\r\nI saw that because also I want to avoid this case:\r\n\r\n<img width=\"195\" alt=\"screen shot 2017-01-25 at 19 45 17\" src=\"https://cloud.githubusercontent.com/assets/2096101/22304218/d8119704-e336-11e6-9ce0-a37a15a5cf5a.png\">\r\n\r\nboom.type → \"Boom Type\"",
